cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper discusses an unsupervised learning approach using autoencoders to learn a latent feature representation of data. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on feature learning and representation, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories.
